messages.messageBody:
Is anyone in the Birmingham area? We are taking a family trip there
to visit my parents & to help my Grandma celebrate her 99th birthday
next month (March 18-30). I'm thinking it might be nice (and a sanity
saver) if we had a homeschool park group to visit. We did visit with
a group last time we were there but I don't remember who/where/when!
My children are ages 9 (ds & pokemon lover) & 6 (dd).

Thanks,
Heather M
tucson az
